Permission is hereby granted, free of charge, to individual developers to use, 
copy, modify, and distribute this software for personal, educational, and 
non-commercial purposes, subject to the following conditions:

PERMITTED USES (No License Required):
- Personal projects and learning
- Educational use and academic research  
- Open source projects (non-commercial)
- Individual developer portfolios
- Personal automation and productivity tools
- Small freelance projects (under $10,000 annual revenue)

COMMERCIAL LICENSE REQUIRED FOR:
- Business use in companies with 5+ employees
- Integration into commercial software products
- SaaS platforms serving external customers
- Resale or redistribution as part of commercial products
- Enterprise environments requiring support/warranty
- Revenue-generating applications using NLCLI

The Commercial License provides:
- Removal of attribution requirements
- Priority support and maintenance
- Custom feature development
- Enterprise deployment assistance
- Legal protections for commercial use

For Commercial License inquiries, please contact: license@nlcli.dev

Enterprise Support
==================

Enterprise support plans are available for organizations requiring:
- Service Level Agreements (SLA)
- Custom integrations and features
- On-premises deployment assistance
- Training and consultation services
- Priority bug fixes and security updates

Contact: enterprise@nlcli.dev for enterprise support options.